  <i>The Kite Runner</i>
</b> did for Afghanistan."<br />"Heart-wrenching, powerful story that portrays heroism and hope under the worst circumstances!"<br />"As a fan of <b>
  <i>The Book Thief,</i>
</b> I really enjoyed this read."<br />"Moving tale of how war effects children! I have seen the war reported on the news, but this book really brings it home how it has affected families on a day to day basis."</span>
