              <span id="reviewTextContainer3296117389" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12080801376849513601">This is not the kind of book that I would usually go for. The story is heartbreaking and you get a deep and profound feeling of what war does. Some of the things in this book are hard to read but there&apos;s something about the way Habib tells the story that keeps pulling you forward - rooting for the main characters. </span>
  <span id="freeText12080801376849513601" style="display:none">This is not the kind of book that I would usually go for. The story is heartbreaking and you get a deep and profound feeling of what war does. Some of the things in this book are hard to read but there's something about the way Habib tells the story that keeps pulling you forward - rooting for the main characters. </span>
